Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.37,0:01:56.07,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Elen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.13,0:02:02.01,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.61,0:02:03.35,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.26,0:02:08.97,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I just wanted to see the face you'd make if you were called that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.46,0:02:35.13,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You've... found him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.91,0:02:41.49,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.49,0:02:42.39,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where's Scythe?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.34,0:02:53.24,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes, I appreciate the car you sent to pick me up,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.24,0:02:54.49,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Colonel Roshunenko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.49,0:02:59.03,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, it's an honor for me that you remember my name,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:00.50,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Doctor Giuseppe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:04.74,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Being addressed by that name makes me recall the times in Moscow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.39,0:03:11.05,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But to see such an able person as you cornered and fleeing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.05,0:03:14.26,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Fieldwork differs quite a lot from working in a laboratory, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.91,0:03:18.25,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"There's a tide in the affairs of men."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.25,0:03:19.50,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.50,0:03:21.77,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's from Shakespeare.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.52,0:03:25.76,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Their tide is mine as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:28.78,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The things I must create here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.32,0:03:31.76,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...have been created.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.07,0:03:39.99,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There is some unusual activity around a weapons dealer, Roshunenko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:43.81,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He seems to be Scythe's old acquaintance,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.81,0:03:47.74,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but these days he runs a territory here at San Francisco's gulf region.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:51.28,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Scythe has been spotted heading this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.28,0:03:55.45,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So basically that snake bastard is trying to make his escape from somewhere around San Francisco.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:00.03,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Clau?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.94,0:04:07.73,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:13.48,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you understand what you're doing, Clau?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:18.64,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He helped Phantom, who pointed her gun at us, escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:22.48,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And yet you're telling me to bring him along?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.48,0:04:24.50,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.39,0:04:33.47,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.19,0:04:35.25,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're such an elusive woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.48,0:04:38.00,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That goes for both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:41.99,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will be the one giving orders at the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.99,0:04:44.00,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The place Scythe is heading to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.00,0:04:46.68,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...is Woodland pier on East Bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:52.07,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It seems some of Roshunenko's men are posted there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:54.70,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:56.70,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.14,0:05:03.76,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Make sure you kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.31,0:05:06.61,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.48,0:05:29.23,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A pity we could not get Zwei, 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:37.08,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but considering the situation, we can do nothing about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.08,0:05:39.65,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That fox can have Zwei. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.41,0:05:43.70,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.88,0:05:47.45,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...why did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.57,0:06:01.59,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Since when did you start asking questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.72,0:06:06.13,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm... sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.50,0:06:14.10,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is there something wrong, comrade Roshunenko?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.86,0:06:20.94,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.64,0:06:24.11,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We've been found?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:34.91,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Indeed, you need not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.91,0:06:38.98,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My personal staff will entertain the people that wish to see us off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.77,0:06:42.59,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You are sending us backup?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.59,0:06:44.76,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I thank you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.69,0:06:47.68,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will see you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.94,0:06:55.07,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}By sending a few extra men, he wants me to owe him a favor, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.13,0:06:56.55,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.32,0:07:03.63,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Will you still be able to live up to my expectations?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.63,0:07:04.82,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ein...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.20,0:07:09.18,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.02,0:07:13.08,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's an appropriate adornment for tonight's little stage show. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.73,0:07:15.65,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There are two spare magazines.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.57,0:07:19.08,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As you know, it's a gun with a quite powerful recoil.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.17,0:07:22.33,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Try to avoid rapid shots if possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.89,0:07:23.69,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.69,0:07:25.31,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Finish it with diligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.31,0:07:27.31,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This will be your last mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:28.80,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.09,0:07:42.47,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Miss Garland will arrive at the pier at any moment now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.47,0:07:45.47,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm certain she will carry out the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.47,0:07:48.69,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I heard you let Zwei tag along too? 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:49.20,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Quite so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.20,0:07:53.11,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He is a man who betrayed Inferno once.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.11,0:07:56.36,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If this proves to be of harm to the organization,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.36,0:07:59.61,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will accept any punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.61,0:08:03.10,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you put that much trust in Zwei?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.10,0:08:06.11,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If there is something I put trust into,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:07.21,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}that would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.86,0:08:11.05,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...that someone who killed only because he was ordered to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:15.11,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...wants to kill a person of his own free will for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.11,0:08:17.47,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's something he longs for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.11,0:08:26.96,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To be honest, I still have my doubts...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.96,0:08:29.56,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...whether I should set you free with a gun in your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.18,0:08:32.24,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}True...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.02,0:08:34.68,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}One round ready to be fired,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:36.76,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}fifteen rounds in the magazine. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.76,0:08:40.00,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If I killed everyone here, I'd still have bullets left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:41.78,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:54.47,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What're you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:58.01,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I won't be able to fight you off with just one round.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.90,0:09:02.39,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But this will be just enough to kill Scythe himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.70,0:09:05.89,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's a pretty big speech for a little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.28,0:09:09.40,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's better than being shot in the back by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.02,0:09:31.91,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.07,0:09:41.33,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That snake bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:51.30,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.92,0:09:57.62,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Scythe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.62,0:09:59.24,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.31,0:10:09.48,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I won't let this slide, you traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.48,0:10:12.59,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't give a shit about number one or two or whatever,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:15.86,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You treated us like pawns...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:18.71,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My brother died because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:23.68,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even if the big shots forgave you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:25.64,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will never...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.25,0:10:30.69,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.75,0:12:00.61,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Elen...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.39,0:12:08.08,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:09.57,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's not too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.94,0:12:13.99,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.03,0:12:15.57,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Together...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.24,0:12:32.40,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Scythe!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.47,0:12:33.97,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.00,0:12:39.14,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.21,0:12:41.70,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well done, Zwei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.62,0:12:45.94,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I always felt you had the potential to surpass Ein someday,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.55,0:12:50.59,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}so I'm not surprised that fox wants you. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.59,0:12:53.32,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Not only did you perfect your skills so quickly, 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.09,0:12:57.05,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but above all, you used Ein as your stepping stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.05,0:12:58.40,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A stepping stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:02.18,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You, of all people, should understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.13,0:13:10.82,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.08,0:13:14.62,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.62,0:13:16.93,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.74,0:13:19.86,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You don't need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:22.94,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If I kill him, Inferno will let you off the hook.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.61,0:13:26.40,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So come with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:31.66,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Elen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.64,0:13:34.98,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.98,0:13:36.41,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kill Zwei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:40.92,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Doing that is the proof you are {\i1}my{\i0} Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.47,0:14:01.73,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's go, Ein!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.43,0:14:08.27,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.33,0:14:12.51,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is how you end up after bragging so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:14.79,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How did you fare?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:17.58,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We managed to clean out most of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.58,0:14:20.78,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There are a lot of casualties, but I'm just peachy as you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.93,0:14:24.94,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.44,0:14:29.81,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're gonna kill Scythe, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.86,0:14:38.30,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've received information that there is a boat docked for us on the fifth pier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.30,0:14:39.65,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}At the southeastern edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.65,0:14:40.02,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.47,0:14:46.54,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Scythe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.19,0:14:52.98,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Come on, you snake bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.98,0:14:54.40,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shoot me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:01.54,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pin her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:03.16,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.16,0:15:04.05,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.25,0:16:24.54,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He's one of Roshunenko's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.89,0:17:36.48,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:13.19,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Scythe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.81,0:18:57.99,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Rei...ji...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:45.60,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Such an interesting outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:47.03,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What a perfect finale.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.23,0:19:57.76,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Elen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.02,0:19:59.76,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.48,0:20:04.03,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.03,0:20:08.67,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I just wanted to see the face you'd make if you were called that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.61,0:20:13.18,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Am I expected to smile at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.08,0:20:15.57,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.57,0:20:17.99,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will make you smile someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:25.00,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It will come back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.00,0:20:27.03,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You will smile when you are happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:28.80,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and cry when you are sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.78,0:20:31.49,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You will be a normal girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.17,0:20:34.49,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.03,0:20:39.96,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So please keep on living until that time comes, Elen.
